RUN VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT DULU

Install Virtual ENV
    pip install virtualenv
    virtualenv -p python3 venv
    run activate.bat di venv/Scripts/activate.bat

Install Flask
    pip install flask

Check installation in env
    pip list

Run Flask Application
    python app.py

Export Flask To Development
    export FLASK_ENV = Development

Buat .ENV di folder root isinya
    FLASK_APP=api.py
    FLASK_ENV=development
    flask run

Kalo nambah library pip jangan lupa nge RUN
    pip freeze > requirement.txt 

Trus install dependency dari requirement.txt
    pip install -r requirements.txt

Linting Error, disable pylint atau add di setting.json
    "python.linting.pylintEnabled": true,
    "python.linting.enabled": false,
    "python.linting.pylintPath": "${workspaceFolder}\\venv\\Scripts\\pylint.exe",

